          "tag": "v1.29.0",
          "name": "v1.29.0",
          "body": "## What's Changed\r\n* fix: treat v1.x as primary branch for npm latest tag (backport #1577) by @felixweinberger in https://github.com/modelcontextprotocol/typescript-sdk/pull/1749\r\n* [v1.x] fix: disallow null (infinite) requested TTL by @LucaButBoring in https://github.com/modelcontextprotocol/typescript-sdk/pull/1339\r\n* [v1.x] fix: add missing size field to ResourceSchema by @olaservo in https://github.com/modelcontextprotocol/typescript-sdk/pull/1575\r\n* Add typings exports by @tdraier in https://github.com/modelcontextprotocol/typescript-sdk/pull/1623\r\n* v1.x npm audit fix by @KKonstantinov in https://github.com/modelcontextprotocol/typescript-sdk/pull/1780\r\n* v1.x #1623 follow up -add missing types to package.json by @KKonstantinov in https://github.com/modelcontextprotocol/typescript-sdk/pull/1773\r\n* [v1.x backport] Allow servers / clients to advertise extensions in the capability object by @localden in https://github.com/modelcontextprotocol/typescript-sdk/pull/1811\r\n* fix(stdio): always set windowsHide on Windows, not just in Electron by @jnMetaCode in https://github.com/modelcontextprotocol/typescript-sdk/pull/1640\r\n* chore: bump version to 1.29.0 by @felixweinberger in https://github.com/modelcontextprotocol/typescript-sdk/pull/1820\r\n\r\n## New Contributors\r\n* @tdraier made their first contribution in https://github.com/modelcontextprotocol/typescript-sdk/pull/1623\r\n* @jnMetaCode made their first contribution in https://github.com/modelcontextprotocol/typescript-sdk/pull/1640\r\n\r\n**Full Changelog**: https://github.com/modelcontextprotocol/typescript-sdk/compare/v1.28.0...v1.29.0",
